Thank you for giving your consent for <%= full_and_preferred_patient_name %> to have their <%= vaccination %>.

Our nursing team has reviewed the answers you gave to the health questions about <%= short_patient_name %> and confirmed it’s safe for <%= short_patient_name %> to have the <%= vaccine_and_method %>.

This will take place at <%= location_name %> on <%= next_session_dates_or %>. Please tell <%= short_patient_name %> that they’ll be vaccinated then.

We’ll let you know once <%= short_patient_name %> is vaccinated.

If <%= short_patient_name_apos %> health changes, or you arrange for them to be vaccinated elsewhere, please let us know. 

<% if vaccine_is_nasal.present? %>^If your child has asthma, please let us know if they have a flare-up of asthma symptoms in the 3 days before the vaccination is due to take place. This includes wheezing or needing to use a reliever inhaler more than usual.<% end %>

You can email <%= subteam_email %> or call <%= subteam_phone %>.
